org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface ListMonitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItemFeatureEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ListMonitorImpl

    public interface ListMonitor
extends ItemFeatureEntry
    A representation of the model object 'List Monitor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Message
    • Message Attribute
    • Default Ack
    • Default Severity
    • Monitor Type
    • Demote Prefix
    • Entries

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getListMonitor()
